[23] Trish Saywell, &quot;Oil: The Danger of Deals with Iraq,&quot; Far Eastern Economic Review, March 6, 2003 [24] Kenneth R. Timmerman, &quot;Rogues Lending Hand to Saddam,&quot; Insight on the News, March 4, 2003. [25] Ibid. [26] Information from Stockholm International Peace Research Institute (SIPRI), &quot;Arms Transfers to Iraq, 1981-2001,&quot; at <!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://projects.sipri.se/armstrade/IRQ_IMPORTS_1982-2001.pdf.">projects.sipri.se/armstra...-2001.pdf.</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
